name: Always a Celebration Multi Gemstone Necklace By Beadique
description: This stunning necklace is sure to become a favorite. The limited edition necklace features Peruvian opal, amethyst, blue chalcedony, appatite and green adventurine stones. The necklace has our custom adjustable clasp that allows the necklace to be worn from 16” to 18” Wear it with a ball gown or a turtleneck collar. It will look great with either.
